{{doc/start}}
Renders one or more visual recipe cards for an item or element, showing inputs, outputs, base craft time, and per-building throughput rates. Backed by [[Module:RecipeCard]].

Use [[Template:RecipeCard Building]] to show all recipes for a specific building, or [[Template:RecipeCard Recipe]] to display a single recipe by its identifier.

== Usage ==
<pre>
{{RecipeCard|id=_base_iron_ingot}}
{{RecipeCard|id=_base_iron_ingot|mode=producing}}
{{RecipeCard|id=_base_iron_ingot|mode=consuming}}
{{RecipeCard|id=_base_iron_ingot|mode=all}}
</pre>

== Parameters ==
{| class="wikitable"
! Parameter !! Description !! Type !! Status
|-
| <code>id</code> || Item or element template identifier (e.g. <code>_base_iron_ingot</code>). || String || Required
|-
| <code>mode</code> || Which recipes to show: <code>producing</code> (default) — recipes that output this item; <code>consuming</code> — recipes that consume it; <code>all</code> — both. || String || Optional
|}

== Notes ==
* Recipe data comes from [[Module:Data/Recipes]] and [[Module:Data/RecipeIndex]].
* Per-building rates (items/minute) are computed from [[Module:Data/RecipeCraftingData]] and displayed with <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code> tooltips showing the item name.
* Elemental inputs/outputs (fluids and gases) are displayed with a litre (<code>L</code>) unit.
* If no matching recipes exist, the template outputs nothing.
{{doc/end}}
